top : shows real time system information, including CPU, memory and process usage
htop : offers additional details such as the user who started the process, the command used to start the process, and the process's start time
df -h : Checks disk space usage 
free -h : shows memory usage, including free, used and swap memory
vmstat : system processes, memory, paging, blockid, traps, and CPU activity
iostat : CPU and I/O statics
date : shows the current date and time
cal : shows the months calender
whoami : who are logged in as

